    <description>
        <p>Sessions is a simple visual timer application designed specifically for the pomodoro
            technique, helping you stay productive by breaking work into focused sessions with
            regular breaks.</p>
        <p>It enables you to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Start focused work sessions with customizable timer durations</li>
            <li>Track your progress with a clean, distraction-free interface</li>
            <li>Take regular breaks to maintain productivity</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

